Hi,

My team really like the Questions plug-in and we want to use it to host questions about a specific topic.  Is there any way we can have specific labels applied to questions when users create them, so that the questions go to the appropriate topic group.

For example, if a user is viewing all questions for a particular topic and they ask a question from within that context, could you apply the current topic label to the Question by default?    This feature would make it easier to keep questions organized and wouldn't rely on users having to remember to apply the correct topics to new questions.  If users don't apply curated labels, they won't reach the appropriate set of Watchers and their question will likely go unanswered.

